<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <title>FoodSavers</title>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <link rel="icon" href="image/img_main/favicon.png" type="image/png" sizes="32x32">
  <link href="css/css_main/style.css" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.3.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
  <link href="css/css_main/animate.css" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link href="css/css_main/waypoints.css" rel="stylesheet" />
  <script src="js/js_main/jquery.waypoints.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
  <script src="js/js_main/waypoints.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.12.9/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.0.8/css/solid.css">
  <script src="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.0.7/js/all.js"></script>
  <script src="js/js_main/wow.min.js"></script>
  <script>
    new WOW().init();
  </script>
  <script> 
    $(document).on('click', 'a[href^="#"]', function (event) {
      event.preventDefault();

      $('html, body').animate({
        scrollTop: $($.attr(this, 'href')).offset().top
      }, 1000);
    });
  </script>
</head>

<body>
  <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-md navbar-dark fixed-top">
    <div class="container-fluid">
      <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">
        <img src="image/img_main/logo.png">
      </a>
      <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbarResponsive">
        <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"> </span>
      </button>
      <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarResponsive">
        <ul class="navbar-nav">
          <li class="nav-item active">
            <a class="nav-link" href="/">Home</a>
          </li>
          <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link" href="#gamesList">Games</a>
          </li>
          <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link" href="/leaderboard">Leaderboard</a>
          </li>
          <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link" href="#about">About</a>
          </li>
          <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link" id="grtVerf"><%=greeting%></a>
          </li>
          <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link" id="navLogout" href='#'></a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <div id="home">
    <div class="landing-text">
      <section class="wow bounceInDown" data-wow-delay="0s">
        <h1>FoodSavers</h1>
      </section>
      <h3>Save Your Food</h3>
      <h4>
        <%= greeting %>
      </h4>
      <a href=<%= lgBtnLnk %> class="btn btn-default btn-lg">
        <%= lgBtn %>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="gamesList">
    <div class="padding">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-6">
            <img src="image/img_main/compost.png" class="wow fadeInUp">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col align-self-center">
                <span id='loVerf' hidden><%= username %></span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-6 text-center align-self-center">
            <h2 class="wow fadeInLeft">Compost Mania</h2>
            <p class="wow fadeInRight" class="lead">Help Paul catch all the falling food waste into the green food bin.
                This game will promote basic knowledge about food composting which is a part of
                reducing the amount of food waste there is in the world. Easy to use controls such as
                moving your mouse or touching the screen if you're on a mobile device. 
                Play Compost Mania to learn more about food composting.</p>
            <button id="game1Btn" type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-lg" onclick="gameBtnControl('game1Btn')">Play</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- modal -->
    <div class="modal fade" id="gameOption" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="Label" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
        <div class="modal-content">
          <div class="modal-header">
            <h5 class="modal-title" id="Label">Play Option</h5>
            <button type="button" id="modalClose" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
              <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
            </button>
          </div>
          <div class="modal-body">
            <p>You are not logged in</p>
          </div>
          <div class="modal-footer">
            <a href="/login" role="button" class="btn btn-primarty">Login</a>
            <button id="modalOk" class="btn btn-success">Play as Guest</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="padding">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-6">
            <img src="image/img_main/groceryshop.png" class="wow fadeInUp">
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-6 text-center align-self-center">
            <h2 class="wow fadeInLeft">Wise Shopping</h2>
            <p class="wow fadeInRight" class="lead">Help Sam with buying food at a grocery store by preventing them from buying too much food.
                Buying too much food will result in food waste which is a major concern we should avoid doing.
                If you put back too much food, you will lose and if the timer runs out you will also lose for 
                buying too much food. Match the amount of food on the shopping list to advance to the next level.
                Play Wise Shopping to help Sam buy food for their family and reduce food waste.</p>
            <button id="game2Btn" type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-lg" onclick="gameBtnControl('game2Btn')">Play</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="padding">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-6">
            <img src="image/img_main/tree_save3.png" class="wow fadeInUp">
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-6 text-center align-self-center">
            <h2 class="wow fadeInLeft">Tree Saviour</h2>
            <p class="wow fadeInRight" class="lead">Help the wandering knight Leo, defend the Tree of Life from the lifeeaters while helping the great tree grow faster by allowing compost to reach the tree to save the world from destruction.</p>
              <button id="game3btn" type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-lg" onclick="gameBtnControl('game3Btn')">Play</button>
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="fixed"></div>

  <div id="about" class="padding">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-12">
          <h4 id="aboutheading">Who We Are...</h4>
          <p>We are a group dedicated to reducing the amount of food waste. What we have seen is that many 
              youth do not know much about how food waste affects our world such as wasting 
              precious resources that our Earth may not be able to support for much longer.
              We wish to bring awareness about food waste to the world with our games.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-6">
          <p><img src="image/img_main/poster.jpeg" class="wow fadeInUp"></p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-6">
          <div id="video" class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9">
              <iframe class="embed-responsive-item" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ia69Ajw8-cU" allow="autoplay; encrypted-media" allowfullscreen></iframe>
          </div>
          <br />
          <div id="video" class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9">
            <iframe class="embed-responsive-item" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/j4aMeW47s40" allow="autoplay; encrypted-media" allowfullscreen></iframe>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  

